Name: Project: Swap
About the game: This is just another free to play first person shooter game on Steam which there are plenty of already. The basic idea is that if you kill another player you teleport to their location. Maybe that idea needs a bit of polishing but I rely on your feedback. Project: Swap is just a game that I made because I wanted to. This game is nothing special and I just want to focus on having fun developing it. Also I want you the players to give me new ideas and lots of feedback Features that I might consider adding Character customization New weapons (Some sort of laser rifle) New maps 3p animation rework
